---
title: "_setReceiver (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_checkDuplicate: receiver == s_receiver
    q_checkDuplicate --> q_revert: receiver unchanged
    q_checkDuplicate --> q_store: receiver changed
    q_revert --> [*]: revert Errors.ValueNotUpdated()
    q_store --> q_emit: s_receiver = receiver
    q_emit --> [*]: emit ReceiverSet(receiver)

    note right of q_checkDuplicate
        INV-001: receiver can be set to address(0) to disable forwarding
        INV-002: setting same receiver address is rejected
    end note
